                    <span>Here is a manual of style that makes sense, is short, and to the point.  All business persons and college students should have a copy of Strunk & White.  ....and don't just use it as a reference; read it from front to back.  That would probably take about 1 hour.  You will gain more common sense grammatical knowledge from this book than a year of English classes.
<br />
<br />Bottom line:  Don't throw away Chicago, but Strunk and White is light, easy to read, and just plain makes sense!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">instructive and witty</div>
                    <div>
